node.text: Celebrated wife’s birthday. Happy Birthday @iamyellowbeak ! Tiamo sempre! Had to celebrate at home due to the ongoing Pandemic restrictions. And we had a series of home delivery feasts and drinks to celebrate this special day. Dry aged steak, grilled octopus legs with Greek salad, flat bread, cold cut platters (courtesy of @xanthloon ), our favorite fizzy wine Moscato di Asti, Super Stacked cake, Cremino and Gianduiotto chocolates. All was good! #circuitbreakersg #covid19 #stayhomestaysafe #celebratewifebirthday #bedrockbarandgrill #bakalakigreektaverna #wineconnectionsg #venchichocolate #venchisg #venchisingapore #giandujotto #gianduiotto #cremini #awfullychocolate #awfullychocolatesg #awfullychocolatecake #moscatodasti #moscatodiasti
